## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Open the app, log in as `userA@example.com` and create a new document.
2. In another browser or incognito tab, register `userB@example.com`.
3. In `userA`'s dashboard, click "Share", enter `userB@example.com`, select "Editor", and submit.
4. Verify that the document immediately displays on `userB`'s dashboard card list with an "Editor" role badge.
5. Test deleting the document from `userB`'s account to verify access control blocks the delete.
6. Verify database records via local testing.
